# Task queue

When `TASKS.md` is in context, follow the `task-runner` skill
(`.cursor/skills/task-runner/SKILL.md`) — the single source of truth for the workflow.

- Work the unchecked `- [ ]` items under **Queue** one at a time.
- Persist progress in `TASKS.md`: mark `- [x]` only after verification, never in chat alone.
